channel.title: Request Most Commonly Wanted
channel.description:
Well, I'm in a bit of need of some USD cash(or maybe some Rs gp), so I'm going to be making some pay scripts. I want 50 USD cash, lol it'll be hard. I'm not up to date with Runescape since, I rarely play. So what scripts do people commonly would like to buy? It can be very easy or hard. I'll make sure they're very user friendely. (The just press run type of thing). Also, I'll only make it if alot of people agree to it.
Thank you! Mr. WhiteShadow.
P.S - If it's just something easy, then I'll just make f0 free.

item.title: Request Most Commonly Wanted
item.dc:creator: @WhiteShadow WhiteShadow
item.description:
@WhiteShadow wrote:

My PowerChopper is 60% complete just making flawless now, yea the perfection of it is 50%. I still need to test all the options and stuff.

Features.
+AutoColor, AutoTalk, AutoReply(so it talks to people), Anti Ban
+Easy Setup, just position players and press run!
+Forms of course
+Multi User Compatibility
+Very Detailed Progress Report Ea Players(xp gained(accurate), trees chopped(accurate), loads done, activity, wc lvl and worked for)
+Axe head fixing, ents, randoms
+Failsafes(logsout if your axe is broken or you don’t have an axe, no endless loops)
+Option to save random event items. So it only drops logs
+Clicks, Click here to play, just incase you got lag or anything.
+No lag, not much awkward mouse movements

Any suggestions, please post.
